snippet.title: The Etherscape Trailer
snippet.description: Welcome to The Etherscape. A Web3 shared world RPG in which the players control the economy. Become an Etherborn and fight your way through hordes of enemies to find the best loot. Death can slow you down, but it can't stop you!
